Title: aws_ebs_limits: New check which monitors AWS/EBS limits
Level: 1
Component: checks
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
Version: 1.6.0b1
Date: 1551970412
Class: feature

The monitored limits and default limit values are
<ul>
<li>Total Block store snapshots, 100000,</li>
<li>Total Magnetic volumes space, 300 TiB,</li>
<li>Total Provisioned IOPS SSD space: 300 TiB,</li>
<li>Total Provisioned IOPS SSD IO operations per second: 300000,</li>
<li>Total General Purpose SSD space: 300 TiB,</li>
<li>Total Cold HDD space: 300 TiB,</li>
<li>Total Throughput Optimized HDD space: 300 TiB,</li>
</ul>
